<td width="100%"><font class="subject">1. The Beginning  *reposted from old KoR Site*</font></td>
<td align="right" nowrap>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
<tr>
<td><a href="http://www.kor-guild.com/cgi-bin/UltraBoard/UltraBoard.cgi?action=Reply&BID=7&TID=8&PID=8"><img src="http://www.kor-guild.com/UltraBoard/Public/Images/Default/reply_quote.gif" width="104" height="20" border="0" alt="Reply to this topic with quote"></a></td>
<td><img src="http://www.kor-guild.com/UltraBoard/Public/Images/Default/blank.gif" width="4" height="20" border="0" alt=""></td>
<td><a href="http://www.kor-guild.com/cgi-bin/UltraBoard/UltraBoard.cgi?action=ModifyPost&BID=7&TID=8&PID=8"><img src="http://www.kor-guild.com/UltraBoard/Public/Images/Default/edit.gif" width="63" height="20" border="0" alt="Modify your message"></td>
</tr>
